item.title: Help Getting Online [Already PF]
item.dc:creator: @schiffel123 schiffel123
item.description:
@schiffel123 wrote:

Either way google for a program that lets you check if your ports are open or not, if they’re closed, try 5555 or re-add 43594 UDP/TCP.
Or just buy a decent VPS, all of them are portforwarded automatically.(Mine did.)
